import { Banner, Names, Text } from "./styles"; import { Heading, Paragraph, Subheading } from "../../components/Text"; import Grid from "../../components/Grid"; import React from "react"; export default () => ( John Newton, Elizabeth Fry, Charles Wesley, Lord Shaftesbury... {/* All over the world when people give an example of how God has changed the world, they start talking about London. */} As they preached, served, reformed, prayed, stood, lived and died by faith in the gospel of Jesus Christ, the heroes of London's church history have inspired believers to make history ever since.

Christian Heritage London exists to tell the gospel by telling their stories to our generations - because history hasn't finished. );
